Description: Terminal-first multi-cloud CLI for cloud practitioners
 Kloud Kompass delivers interactive, human-friendly access to AWS
 services across cost tracking, compute inventory, networking,
 storage, IAM, databases, and security auditing.
 .
 Built for terminal practitioners who prefer shell workflows over GUIs,
 it provides a blazingly fast TUI and a feature-rich dashboard.
